    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303320/extras/5734cbfebc661446852dbae9610f7e7e.poster.avif?t=1772110004\" width=180 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303320/extras/5734cbfebc661446852dbae9610f7e7e.webm?t=1772110004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303320/extras/5734cbfebc661446852dbae9610f7e7e.mp4?t=1772110004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i><strong>&quot;我醒来时感觉█████。这是█████又一个雨夜。我想知道██是否梦境。█████必须逃离。&quot;</strong></i><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303320/extras/e62d9d61c11a3301fbf17e2cb740313d.poster.avif?t=1772110004\" width=180 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303320/extras/e62d9d61c11a3301fbf17e2cb740313d.webm?t=1772110004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303320/extras/e62d9d61c11a3301fbf17e2cb740313d.mp4?t=1772110004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i><strong>“时间似乎以一种███████的方式██。我必须███████。她是我的女朋友吗？&quot;</strong></i><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303320/extras/32953b255021f51dad9ec753be29ec1b.poster.avif?t=1772110004\" width=180 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303320/extras/32953b255021f51dad9ec753be29ec1b.webm?t=1772110004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303320/extras/32953b255021f51dad9ec753be29ec1b.mp4?t=1772110004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i><strong>&quot; 一声巨响。我想可能又是████，██████████。我应该████问问，我是否█████。&quot;</strong></i><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303320/extras/92725f8256b6546a0bbf0c904f86de4c.poster.avif?t=1772110004\" width=180 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303320/extras/92725f8256b6546a0bbf0c904f86de4c.webm?t=1772110004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303320/extras/92725f8256b6546a0bbf0c904f86de4c.mp4?t=1772110004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i><strong>&quot;████机器人。███已经疯了。███犯下了谋杀案？如果█正在失去██理智该怎么办。&quot;</strong></i><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303320/extras/25e3cc4001af17d713ec0e0ecde95d71.poster.avif?t=1772110004\" width=180 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303320/extras/25e3cc4001af17d713ec0e0ecde95d71.webm?t=1772110004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303320/extras/25e3cc4001af17d713ec0e0ecde95d71.mp4?t=1772110004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i><strong>“███ ██ █████ ██ ██████ ██ █████ ██ ██ 死亡 ███ ██.&quot;</strong></i><br><br><br>《Three Minutes To Eight》的故事背景设定在不久的未来，这款烧脑的像素风格冒险游戏打破常规，设计出引人入胜的曲折情节：主角注定在晚上07:57遇难。然而，主角仍有逃过一劫的机会。你将需要揭露真相、发现秘密通道、设法逃避死亡，并解锁多种结局。每次游玩都有不同的体验，各种随机元素和独特事件诱惑你多次重玩，发现其中所有的隐藏之谜。体验不断变化的游戏，沉浸在摇摇欲坠的边缘状态意识中——一切皆有可能，却又始终难以捉摸。",
